# streams-pipeline

Synchronous iterator pipeline — `Range.map.filter.foldLeft` chain.
Cross-backend: lowers to `Iterable`/`Range` HOFs on every backend
(JVM scala-cli, JS Array, ssc interp/JIT, rust iterator chain).

```scalascript
def workload(): Int =
  (1 to 10)
    .map(x => x * 2)
    .filter(x => x % 3 == 0)
    .foldLeft(0)((sum, x) => sum + x)
```
